panelDataJavascriptCode.code:
if (record.div < 0.5) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.PINK
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.JUNGLE_GREEN
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
}

panelDataJavascriptCode.name: New Panel Data Javascript Code
panelDataJavascriptCode.code:
if (record.thresholdVal == 2) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.APPLE_GREEN
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else if (record.thresholdVal == 3) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.TRUE_ORANGE
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else if (record.thresholdVal == 4) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.TRUE_RED
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.TRUE_GREEN
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
}
